課程大綱

「流體力學」延伸「基礎熱流學一、二」中流體力學部分的內容。本課程涵蓋: Review of the Euler’s Equations/Navier-Stokes Equations; Some Basic, Plane Potential Flows; Review of Internal Flow; Flow over Immersed Bodies (Boundary Layer Flow); Compressible Flow.  課程說明(Course Description)「流體力學」延伸「基礎熱流學一、二」中流體力學部分的內容。本課程涵蓋: Review of the Euler’s Equations/Navier-Stokes Equations; Some Basic, Plane Potential Flows; Review of Internal Flow; Flow over Immersed Bodies (Boundary Layer Flow); Compressible Flow.指定用書(Text Books)Fundamentals of Fluid Mechanics" by B. R. Munson, D. F. Young and T. H.Okiishi, 6th Ed., 2010, John Wiley. 參考書籍(References)"Fluid Mechanics" by Y.A. Cengel and J.M. Cimbala, 2006, Mcgraw-Hill.教學方式(Teaching Method)課堂講授及專題實驗教學進度(Syllabus)1. Review of the Euler’s Equations/Navier-Stokes Equations2. Some Basic, Plane Potential Flows3. Review of Dimensional Analysis4. Internal Flow5. Flow over Immersed Bodies (Boundary Layer Flow)6. Compressible Flow (including a supersonic nozzle experiment)成績考核(Evaluation)Midterm exam (35%)Final exam (35%)Homework, Quizzes and Experiment (30%)



回頂端








課程內容



第1講 Introduction Velocity Field
第2講 Velocity and Acceleration Fields Revisited
第3講 Inviscid Flow ＆Uniform Flow
第4講 Other Aspects of Potential Flow Analysis
第5講 Steady Laminar Flow Between Fixed Parallel plates  
第6講 DimensionlessGroups in Fluid MechanicsGroups Mechanics  
第7講 Flow Around Immersed Bodies
第8講 From F=ma Applied Directly to a Fluid Element  
第9講 Turbulent shear stress  
第10講 Chapter 9 Introduction  
第11講 Prandtl/BlasiusBoundary Layer Solution  
第12講 Pressure Drag  
第13講 Surface Pressure Distribution  
第14講 Category of compressible flow  
第15講  Converging–Diverging Duct Flow  
第16講  Adiabatic constant area duct flow with friction (Fannoflow)  









 關鍵字

流體力學(Fluid Dynamics)
簡介速度場(Introduction Velocity Field)
加速度場(Fields Revisited)
無粘流均勻流(Inviscid Flow ＆Uniform Flow)
湍流剪應力(Turbulent shear stress )
可壓縮流的類別(Category of compressible flow )
縮擴管流(Converging–Diverging Duct Flow )

